<span style="color: #000000;"><strong> Kent Kovboyu &#8211; Method Man</strong></span><br />
<span style="color: #000000;"><strong> Peaky Blinders &#8211; Daniel Fearn,</strong></span><br />
<span style="color: #000000;"><strong> Sniper: Duvar &#8211; Josh Kemble,</strong></span><br />
