<span class="primewp-featured-post-likes primewp-featured-post-header-meta"><a href="#" class="themesdna-likes" id="themesdna-likes-13834" title="Like this"><span class="themesdna-likes-count">4</span></a></span>            <span class="primewp-featured-post-views primewp-featured-post-header-meta"><span class="themesdna-views" id="themesdna-views-13834" title="805 Views">805</span></span></div></div><h3 class="primewp-fp01-post-title"><a href="https://www.seslendirme.org/alp-bugdayci/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Alp Buğdaycı">Alp Buğdaycı</a></h3><div class="primewp-fp01-post-snippet primewp-fp-post-snippet primewp-fp01-post-excerpt primewp-fp-post-excerpt"><p>Alp Buğdaycı  Vefatının 10. yılında Alp Buğdaycı&#8217;yı saygı ve rahmetle anıyoruz. Doğum Tarihi : 21 Temmuz 1964 Doğum Yeri : Diyarbakır  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1980’de ailesiyle İstanbul’a geldi. 1981’de, haftalık müzik&#8230;</p></div></div><div class="primewp-fp01-post"><div class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail">
<a href="https://www.seslendirme.org/erol-kardeseci/" title="Permanent Link to Erol Kardeseci" class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail-link"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iODAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxMDAgODAiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=" width="100" height="80" data-src="https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/erol-kardeseci.png" class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail-img wp-post-image" alt="" title="Erol Kardeseci" decoding="async" loading="lazy" data-srcset="https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/erol-kardeseci.png 274w, https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/erol-kardeseci-200x160.png 200w" data-sizes="auto, (max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px" /></a><div class="primewp-featured-post-header primewp-clearfix">
<span class="primewp-featured-post-likes primewp-featured-post-header-meta"><a href="#" class="themesdna-likes" id="themesdna-likes-39175" title="Like this"><span class="themesdna-likes-count">1</span></a></span>            <span class="primewp-featured-post-views primewp-featured-post-header-meta"><span class="themesdna-views" id="themesdna-views-39175" title="542 Views">542</span></span></div></div><h3 class="primewp-fp01-post-title"><a href="https://www.seslendirme.org/erol-kardeseci/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Erol Kardeseci">Erol Kardeseci</a></h3><div class="primewp-fp01-post-snippet primewp-fp-post-snippet primewp-fp01-post-excerpt primewp-fp-post-excerpt"><p>Erol Kardeseci Doğum Tarihi : 6- Ekim-1936 Ölüm Tarihi : 15 Mayıs 2012 Eğitimi : 1961 yılında Devlet Konservatuvarını bitirdi. 1961 yılında develt konservatuvarını bitiren Erol Kardeseci, Ankara Devlet Tiyatrosunda uzun yıllar çalıştıktan&#8230;</p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="primewp-featured-posts-widget-one-id-4" class="primewp-side-widget widget primewp-box primewp-featured-posts-widget-one"><div class="primewp-box-inside"><div class="primewp-widget-header"><h2 class="primewp-widget-title"><span>SESLENDİRME DUBLAJ</span></h2></div><div class="primewp-fp01-posts"><div class="primewp-fp01-post"><div class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail">
<a href="https://www.seslendirme.org/sesli-sinemaya-gecis-ve-dublajin-dogusu/" title="Permanent Link to Sesli Sinemaya Geçiş ve Dublajın Doğuşu" class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail-link"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTAwIDEwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" width="100" height="100" data-src="https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/sinemada-seslendirme-100x100.jpg" class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail-img wp-post-image" alt="Sinemada Seslendirme" title="Sesli Sinemaya Geçiş ve Dublajın Doğuşu" decoding="async" loading="lazy" data-srcset="https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/sinemada-seslendirme-100x100.jpg 100w, https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/sinemada-seslendirme-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/sinemada-seslendirme-480x480.jpg 480w" data-sizes="auto, (max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px" /></a><div class="primewp-featured-post-header primewp-clearfix">
<span class="primewp-featured-post-likes primewp-featured-post-header-meta"><a href="#" class="themesdna-likes" id="themesdna-likes-93991" title="Like this"><span class="themesdna-likes-count">49</span></a></span></div></div><h3 class="primewp-fp01-post-title"><a href="https://www.seslendirme.org/sesli-sinemaya-gecis-ve-dublajin-dogusu/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Sesli Sinemaya Geçiş ve Dublajın Doğuşu">Sesli Sinemaya Geçiş ve Dublajın Doğuşu</a></h3><div class="primewp-fp01-post-footer">
<span class="primewp-fp01-post-meta primewp-fp01-post-date"><i class="far fa-clock"></i>&nbsp;11-Oca-2026</span></div><div class="primewp-fp01-post-snippet primewp-fp-post-snippet primewp-fp01-post-excerpt primewp-fp-post-excerpt"><p>Sesli Sinemaya Geçiş ve Dublajın Doğuşu 1920’li yılların sonu, sinema tarihinin belki de en çarpıcı ve dönüştürücü dönemlerinden birine tanıklık etmiştir. Yaklaşık otuz yıl boyunca tamamen sessiz bir görsel anlatım biçimi olarak gelişen&#8230;</p></div></div><div class="primewp-fp01-post"><div class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail">
<a href="https://www.seslendirme.org/dunyada-ve-turkiyede-seslendirme/" title="Permanent Link to Dünyada ve Türkiye’de Seslendirme" class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail-link"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTAwIDEwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" width="100" height="100" data-src="https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/turkiyede-seslendirme-100x100.jpg" class="primewp-fp01-post-thumbnail-img wp-post-image" alt="Türkiye&#039;de seslendirme" title="Dünyada ve Türkiye’de Seslendirme" decoding="async" loading="lazy" data-srcset="https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/turkiyede-seslendirme-100x100.jpg 100w, https://www.seslendirme.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/turkiyede-seslendirme-150x150.jpg 150w" data-sizes="auto, (max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px" /></a><div class="primewp-featured-post-header primewp-clearfix">
